				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Ok, Ill admite this line of spells does not seem to be useful at first but by using the proper tecniques and experamentation it can be mastered. I generally use this spell in OT and have been just as successful with beguile(this ones just a little more convenent.  I like to snare the creature then charm him.  Then I snare another animal,send my pet in and fear the creature so my pet can slaughter him with little to no injury while I med. when Charm wheres I simply recharm..I have gotten a green tigress to take out a blue tiger with this tecnique using one bubble of mana. There is some down sides, If both creature are almost dead and your charm fades you must recharm or the creature will poof (infact if you kill em both they will both poof) because you knowlonger control the pet and therefore did less than half dmg.
				</font>
